<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: latha;
            color:white;
            background: linear-gradient( 
            rgba(0,0,0,0.65),rgba(0,0,0,0.65),rgba(0,0,0,0.38),rgba(0,0,0,0)
            )
            background-image: url("foodd");
            background-size: cover;
        }
        .box{ width: 900px;
              float:right;
               border:1px solid black;
            }

        .box ul li{
            width: 120px;
            float:right;
            margin: 10px auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .box ul li a{ text-decoration:none;
                      color:darkgray;
                    }
        
        .box ul li:hover {  background-color:green; }
        .box ul li a:hover { color:white; }
        
        .wd {
            width: 300px;
            height: 539px;
            background-color: black;
            opacity: 0.9;
            padding: 55px;
        }

        .wd h1{
            text-align: center;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 100px;
        }

        .wd h4{
            text-align: justify;
            color:darkgray;
            font-weight: normal;
        }
    
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="box">
    <ul type="none">
        <li><%= link_to 'Signup', signup_path %></li>
        <li><%= link_to 'Login', login_path %></li>
    </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="wd">
        <h1>Welcome</h1>
        <h4>We give our user the top priority. The website is created to give a user 
        the best experience. The UI is user friendly and easy to navigate. 
        To make a reservation a user needs to sign-up or sign-in.</h4>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 


